Merge pull request #134 from jopt-simple/localized-exception-messages

Ensure getMessage is consistent across Locales

commit.message:
Ensure getMessage is consistent across Locales

OptionException.getMessage should return the same message regardless
of the runtime Locale. It users want locale-specific exception
messages, they should can OptionException.getLocalgetLocalizedMessage.

This requires making a copy of the default message bundle for the
English locale.

Fixes #132
